Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.58,0:00:10.72,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.97,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:59.03,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(187,1)}The Eye of the Midnight Sun's Secret
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.63,0:02:23.09,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you've heard, but apparently the \NQueen of Witches from the Witches' Forest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.09,0:02:25.12,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,has cured Asta's arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:28.59,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Such wonderful news. I was \Nso worried, I couldn't slee—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:30.66,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.66,0:02:32.65,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I had no trouble sleeping at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.65,0:02:37.97,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you two were {\i1}so{\i0} worried,\Nbut I'm sure you're both relieved now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:40.59,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't worried about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:41.84,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Neither was I!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:46.89,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,But Klaus, you were dumping water over \Nyourself every night and praying for Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:51.40,flashback,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,May Asta's arms get better! \NMay Asta's arms get better!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:53.36,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,H-How did you know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.36,0:02:58.22,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I was also going to pray, \Nbut you were already ther—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:03:01.42,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, never mind! I didn't see a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.42,0:03:04.91,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't, either! I didn't douse\N myself with water and pray!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:06.16,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chan—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:07.16,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:11.54,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you know why I called you two here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:13.67,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,You got serious so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:15.67,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,This is about the Eye of the Midnight Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:20.07,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,They showed up in the Witches' Forest \Nand attempted to take the magic stone
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:21.80,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,that belonged to the Queen of Witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:26.68,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Thankfully, Asta and the others faced them \Nand were able to obtain the magic stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:29.09,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta's amazing, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:34.06,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know when or where we might end \Nup fighting the Eye of the Midnight Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:37.69,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why... we're going to have an \NEye of the Midnight Sun study session!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.06,0:03:41.57,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,First, Yuno, tell me everything you \Nknow about the Eye of the Midnight Sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:44.08,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,What I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:47.83,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they suddenly attacked \Nthe royal capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:01.66,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,We Magic Knights went to face them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.25,0:04:04.47,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,See if you can take my magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:07.26,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Magic: Spiral Flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:10.56,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Magic: Sol Linea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:18.71,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Steel Creation Magic: Fierce Spiral Lance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:22.61,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,Glass Creation Magic: Verre Fleur!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:29.45,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,Sand Creation Magic: \NSand-Armored Heavy Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:33.79,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,If you're hurt, please come see me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:36.95,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Creation Magic: Raging Mother Goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:43.66,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I will not allow anyone to touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:48.22,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Briar Creation Magic: \NCorpse-Hunting Briar Trees!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:53.18,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Slashing Sea Serpent!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:55.60,main,Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,Mist Magic: Solid Mist Clones!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:58.69,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Accept your punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:02.05,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Mercury Magic: Rain of Silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:07.03,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Punishment for the crime of \Ndaring to threaten the people
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:08.87,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:12.91,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Creation Magic: Leo Rugiens!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:17.33,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Burn to ashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:18.31,main,Man A,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:19.49,main,Woman A,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.49,0:05:21.32,main,Man B,0000,0000,0000,,They're so powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:23.80,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Let me just tell you one thing about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:25.95,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:28.76,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,hate losing more than anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:32.39,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Wind Spirit Magic: Sylph's Breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.47,0:05:37.90,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,But what the enemy was truly after
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:42.26,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,was the captain of the \NCrimson Lion Kings, Fuegoleon Vermillion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.85,0:05:47.05,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:04.34,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:09.54,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Despite how strong Fuegoleon is, \Nwe don't know when he'll wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.71,0:06:13.43,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,That was a miscalculation on my part.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:16.85,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,No, this was due to our inexperience.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:22.11,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,We've confirmed that the pendant \NFuegoleon was wearing is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:25.50,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,The jewels embedded into that stone slab...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:35.34,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Next, the Eye of the Midnight Sun \Nappeared near the town of Nean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:37.45,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Asta and a few others who were \Non break met them there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:41.37,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that Asta was fated to cross \Npaths with the Eye of the Midnight Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:46.96,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,In Nean, the leader of the Eye of \Nthe Midnight Sun, Licht, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.63,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to introduce them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.98,0:06:52.85,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,They are the strongest three \Nin the Eye of the Midnight Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:55.31,top,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,The Third Eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:55.31,sign_19644_200_Third_Eye,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Third Eye
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:07:00.23,top,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,With a name meaning the opposite\Nof faith, Raia the Disloyal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:07:00.23,sign_20632_210_Raia_the_Disloya,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(757,1)}Raia the Disloyal
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:04.98,top,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,With a name meaning the opposite\Nof hope, Vetto the Despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:04.98,sign_20632_210_Raia_the_Disloya,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(757,1)}Vetto the Despair
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:10.65,top,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,And with a name meaning the opposite\Nof love, Fana the Hateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:10.65,sign_20632_210_Raia_the_Disloya,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(757,1)}Fana the Hateful
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:13.16,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's about time we end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:15.61,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.61,0:07:19.08,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit Magic: Salamander's Breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:28.34,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Despite how powerful Captain Yami is,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:31.55,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,the strongest three of the Eye of \Nthe Midnight Sun gave him trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:42.38,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're having fun, Yami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.38,0:07:43.98,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Let us play, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:48.65,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man... Another second or two, \Nand something would've awakened in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:52.61,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed you can even say those \Nwords when you look like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:56.83,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, how pathetic are you that \Nyou actually have to rely on us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:08:01.08,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Jack the Ripper from \Nthe Green Praying Mantises,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:04.37,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Nozel Silva from the Silver Eagles,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:08.05,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,and Captain Charlotte Roselei from the \NBlue Rose Knights came to assist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.37,0:08:11.30,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Briar Creation Magic: \NCorpse-Hunting Briar Trees!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:16.57,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Severing Magic: Death Scythe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:20.39,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,The one I have business with is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:23.06,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Mercury Magic: Silver Spears!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:37.91,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I finally weakened him this much. \NThere's no way I'm letting him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:41.91,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you'd try that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:43.41,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.72,0:08:46.63,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You're after the leader's head, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:48.47,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Go on. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:51.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not giving up...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:55.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,...is my magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:08.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you like that? No magic in that attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.43,0:09:11.23,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:12.82,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:16.07,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have that grimoire?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:18.32,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:21.63,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,have the Demon-Slayer Sword \Nand the Demon-Dweller Sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:25.96,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Those swords belong to the master!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:30.50,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This crappy grimoire and these \Ncrappy swords belong to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:31.99,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.54,0:09:34.63,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,That grimoire is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:41.81,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,If this keeps up, you won't last, Licht!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:46.18,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Trinity Sealing Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:52.17,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,You worked a little too hard there, Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:58.45,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Our boss isn't feeling too good, \Nso we're gonna head home for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:02.78,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,The next time we meet, \NI'll show you what true despair is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:05.58,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,And that will be the end of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:10.30,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,We, the Eye of the Midnight Sun,\Nare always watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:18.63,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,They were somehow able to fight \Noff Licht and the Third Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:22.97,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,If I had been there, everything \Nwould've been easier for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:24.64,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,They wouldn't have been so badly hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.09,0:10:26.42,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,After further investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:31.19,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,we were able to determine why they were \Nafter Captain Fuegoleon's pendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:36.38,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,They call the stones that were \Nset into it "magic stones."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.38,0:10:38.84,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,They believe that if they \Ncollect all of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:41.95,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,they will be reborn into their true forms,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:45.12,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,which are linked closely to mana, \Nand gain enormous power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:47.70,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently they also went after Fuegoleon
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:51.17,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,because they wanted the \Nmagic stone that he had.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:54.13,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,There are three magic stones left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.56,0:10:58.09,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,They know the location of one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:10:59.34,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,And where's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:01.63,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,In a strong magic region...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.63,0:11:03.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The Underwater Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.69,0:11:07.54,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So you want us to get there before \Nthe Eye of the Midnight Sun does
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:10.52,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,and snatch the magic stone or whatever?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:12.44,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Yami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:13.94,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,And you, Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.37,0:11:15.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.05,0:11:23.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I got too excited and \Nknocked the air out of myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:24.67,top,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen someone \Nself-destruct from saluting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:29.57,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,And then the Black Bulls headed \Nto the Underwater Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:31.32,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.32,0:11:33.73,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,He should've just given me the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.73,0:11:37.95,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the Wizard King is \Nrather fond of Asta, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:39.05,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:42.13,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Once the Black Bulls arrived \Nat the Underwater Temple,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:43.59,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,they searched for the magic stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:47.25,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,But the Eye of the Midnight \NSun arrived again,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.25,0:11:51.39,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,and one of the members of the most powerful \NThird Eye, Vetto the Despair, appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:54.86,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:12:00.11,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you let us join in?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:12.75,italics,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We'll hit him with all the magic we've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:17.04,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Combo Magic: Flame Lightning \NExplosive Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:33.30,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Now... scream! Despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:39.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ib I gwabe up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:41.28,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Fu curd I brotec?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:42.28,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.34,0:12:50.54,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,He said, "If I gave up, who could I protect?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:57.81,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? All this power
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.81,0:13:00.96,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,from a little bird's song \Nand a mouse's dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:04.30,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Frontier magic is truly intriguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:07.59,italics,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! This spell was \Ncreated because we're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:10.64,italics,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,We served the sea god, praying, \Nsinging and dancing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:15.69,italics,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,We spent a long time that way, \Nweaving the magic into our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:19.15,italics,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Ever since we were \Nlittle, we've offered up this song
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:22.49,italics,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,and dance to the sea god \Nand the rest of our people!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:23.78,italics,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,This spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:26.87,italics,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,...is our bond with the people
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:29.28,italics,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,of the Underwater Temple!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:33.43,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Did they do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:38.25,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:43.30,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:46.55,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams? Bonds?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:50.30,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,You have no right to talk about such things!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.17,0:13:53.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kahono!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:03.11,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,What is this power?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.13,0:14:07.11,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Let my friend go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:09.66,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Girl, you're royalty?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:13.33,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Noelle Silva of the Black Bulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:16.79,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you hurt my friends and comrades?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:22.14,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Sea Dragon's Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:40.77,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:58.89,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive... You managed \Nto draw me out, human.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.43,0:15:01.29,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:03.50,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's payback time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:05.70,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Mythical Beast Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:29.36,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,A-Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.77,0:15:31.10,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.69,0:15:34.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.38,0:15:39.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't given up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:08.91,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Despair...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:15.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You've lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.66,0:16:31.34,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,After working together, they finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:33.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like that, you bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:37.72,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:37.72,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:41.18,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Well done! I'm so proud of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:42.89,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,You're so amazing, la!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:46.27,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... That shrimp is full of guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:51.03,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,This magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:55.62,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking you all down with me... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.62,0:16:58.62,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I'll blow this whole temple to smithereens!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:04.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:07.38,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Right, consider it brought.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.21,0:17:16.68,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you dumbasses. You good?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:18.26,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yami!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:19.76,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Finral...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:21.14,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Vanessa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:22.52,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:23.81,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.17,0:17:25.10,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Charmy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.17,0:17:25.10,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.37,0:17:27.34,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.34,0:17:29.15,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Grey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:32.59,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,And Magna and Luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:35.40,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You guys did good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:38.70,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be nice and take care of the cleanup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:42.45,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, I'm taking all the glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.31,0:17:45.87,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I was able to surpass my limits...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:51.38,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,is because of all of you, you dumbasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:54.86,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.86,0:17:59.97,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,You humans shall taste despair... Despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:03.64,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up with the despair this, despair\Nthat already, you three-eyed goon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:08.22,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter how strong your magic is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:12.82,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,This spell cuts through dimensions!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:22.83,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Magic: Dark Cloaked Dimension Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:35.46,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Consider that my thanks for \Nlooking after my squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:39.09,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, Mister Despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:43.09,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,And then the Black Bulls defeated Vetto
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.09,0:18:45.75,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,and obtained the magic stone that \Nwas at the Underwater Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:47.98,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,They had completed their mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:52.52,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Also, according to the Queen of Witches...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:58.25,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,That magic stone is a magical item \Nthat heightens the wearer's powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.25,0:19:02.12,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,but only those of the elf tribe\N are truly able to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.58,0:19:08.71,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,It could be that the Eye of the Midnight Sun\Nare descendants of the elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:13.15,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,And Asta, the two swords you bear...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:18.11,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,They are the ruined remains of the \Nmagic swords used by the elves' leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.11,0:19:19.32,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Elves?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:22.53,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,They're legendary beings. \NThey actually existed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:28.69,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know what will happen once they've \Ncollected the remaining magic stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.69,0:19:32.47,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter what happens, \Nwe, the Magic Knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.47,0:19:35.32,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,will protect the Clover \NKingdom and its people!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.32,0:19:38.07,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno, Mimosa! I'm counting on you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:39.38,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:43.57,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to worry. No matter \Nthe enemy, I shall defeat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:48.08,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become the \NWizard King. So, Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:51.58,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never going to lose to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:04.26,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,My lot got this from the old \Nhag in the Witches' Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.38,0:20:10.51,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,They defeated the Diamond Kingdom's \Nforces and the Eye of the Midnight Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.51,0:20:14.06,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the Black Bulls did \Nan excellent job again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:15.56,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.08,0:20:21.75,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. But nothing's going to get \N{\i1}star{\i0}ted if we don't get any stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:23.57,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You know, stars. Lotsa stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:26.33,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:31.49,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then... I've received quite a bit \Nof information, both good and bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:35.33,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,The good news is we should be able to find \Nthe Eye of the Midnight Sun's hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:38.74,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? That sure is good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.74,0:20:40.34,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So what's the bad news?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.19,0:20:45.59,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,It appears they're finally \Ngoing to make their move.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:51.60,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like there's going \Nto be another battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:53.56,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Another fight...
