Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.86,0:22:50.10,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.93,0:22:54.89,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Prayers
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.05,0:22:53.25,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.30,0:23:02.21,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,May Asta's arms get better! \NMay Asta's arms get better!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.21,0:23:05.29,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Five hundred and one, five hundred\N and two, five hundred and three...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.13,0:23:09.09,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno, do you want to join me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.09,0:23:09.95,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.95,0:23:11.56,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to be shy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.56,0:23:13.61,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.86,0:23:12.87,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Come, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:29.97,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.91,0:23:36.87,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.63,0:23:42.56,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,It's a festival to announce all of \Nthe Magic Knights' achievements!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.56,0:23:44.90,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,We call it the Star Festival! \NI hope you guys have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.90,0:23:48.69,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 67: \N"A Fun Festival Double Date."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:54.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 67\N\N{\fs18} A Fun Festival Double Date
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.69,0:23:50.82,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,A date, eh? Must be nice to be young.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.82,0:23:53.82,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then. Guess I'll transform \Nso I can wander around.
